# Input

```grit
`var $x = [$names]` => `var coolPeople = [$names]` where {
  $names <: every orelse {`"andrew"`, `"alex"`}
}

```


# Formatted

```grit
`var $x = [$names]` => `var coolPeople = [$names]` where {
	$names <: every orelse {
		`"andrew"`,
		`"alex"`
	}
}

```
